name: Cthulhair
description:
Do not look into the hair. In the hair lies the ways of madness. Instead let this young girl lull you with her calming presence and serene floating squamous eye. She's named him Squamie!

11 x 17 digital print

name: "Your Name" Gallifreyan button
description:
Ever wanted to have your name in Gallifreyan? Want one you can pin to your shirt? Want to have any old phrase or saying in a language only other deep Doctor Who nerds will be able to read? Order a custom button, get a complimentary animated GIF of any phrase you can think of!

Examples of the animated GIFs at http://vanitygames.tumblr.com/post/57282585251/makin-animated-gifs-of-peoples-names-in

name: "Hello Sweetie" gallifreyen button
description: Give the message you've always wanted to give in Gallifreyen with these buttons. Bold gold/orange on a weathered TARDIS blue, let these buttons serve as a mystery and as a secret handshake between true Doctor Who fans.

name: Crits Happen D20 temp tattoo
description: Wear this tattoo on your flexing, bulging muscles to your next game and let everyone at the table know you are seriously commited to crits! Temporary tattoo goes on in seconds, peels off cleanly, no cracking or scrubbing needed.

name: Crits Happen d20 button
description:
2.5" tin and mylar pinback button, faux-tattoo print designed by me to express what should be happening _all the time_.

Roll on, folks. Crits happen!

name: Cthulhu Damask Dice Bag
description: this nearly 5" x 4" square-bottomed dice bag is made from kona cotton in a gorgeous cthulhu damask pattern that I designed. Toggle lock keeps the cord secure, and tiny dice are sewn onto the cord for accent. Entirely handmade.

name: HP & MP bars temporary tattoo
description:
Commitment issues? No worries, these handy dandy temporary tattoos give you all the pleasure of displaying your HP and MP to the world without the commitment of a lifetime of ink on your skin.

HP a little low, you say? No worries, a little tofu or a crunchy chick should fix you right up.

Tattoos go on in seconds, come off just as easily without flaking or scrubbing.

name: Zelda Hearts temporary tattoo
description: Now you can wear your HP on your arm (or any other body part you like). This temporary tattoo goes on fast--just peel off the film and place onto skin, dab with water for 30 seconds. It comes off just as easy, peels off without scrubbing or flaking.

name: Character Portrait Commission
description: Single character, of your description and choosing, and I will draw the ever-loving bajoozles out of it. Flat color, digital art of your RP character or OC or really anything you'd like to see made real.

name: D20 sew-on patch
description:
Made with ink-printed fabric of an original design by me, the D20 design has been pressed onto a stiff backing and then stitched. Entirely handmade, simple and elegant in black and white, durable and long-lasting.

Perfect for your D&D buddies or just sewn onto your dice bag

name: Sparks McGee rebel button
description: The Ballad of Sparks Mcgee: A man both callow and hot, Who, more often than not, Was apt to tell, Nay even yell, "I GOT A COURSE YOU CAN PLOT!" From the legend of Sparks McGee, a tumblr sensation and machismo and charismatic riff on Wesley Crusher, the ensign everyone loves to rag on.

name: Boo Bees mario bros parody button
description: A pun, or a play on words, and a juvenile reference to body parts, and a popular video game reference, what more do you need for comedy gold? Show your beautiful boo bees to the world with this 2.5" pinback button.

name: Anti-possession Tattoo button
description: A compliment to The Anti-Possession Temporary Tattoo, this 2.5" pinback button can keep anything safe that you pin it to. As seen on Supernatural, tattooed on some hot bods to keep them safe and out of demon's way.

name: Bowties Are Cool button
description:
Because they are; carry a bowtie wherever you go, be forever cool like a certain timey wimey lordy guy

This Doctor Who themed button is 2.5" pinbacked with mylar covering, original art by me.

name: Demon Bane from Supernatural temporary tattoo
description: Now you can temporarily hide yourself from demons without having to commit to a lifetime of ink on your skin. This 1.5" by 1.5" temporary tattoos go on in seconds.

name: "Home Is Where The Gaming Is" tee-shirt
description: beautiful faux cross-stitch design of iconic gaming symbols and characters, this White Next Level N6210 Men's CVC Crew is super soft and comfortable and stretchy, a great way to show your comfy cozy gaming love. Also available as a print with even more icons and colors T-shirts fit comfortably (especially with the large sizes). Myself and my housebro are modeling both the large and the XL sizes below, both of us are not tiny people.

name: Love Note for the Wordless print
description:
A beautiful note from someone for whom words flee when faced with their greatest love, emerald ink on pale green background brings vivacious life to this simple message.

This 8 x 10 print will make a gorgeous framed gift for those closest to your heart.

name: Betty and Veronica All Grown Up print
description:
A day at the beach for Betty and Veronica, but while their golden summer youths are past, they still have the world as their oyster. They're all grown up, a little wiser, a little more savvy, but they're still the same old gals at heart.

11" x 17" print

name: Angry Dragon print
description: a riff on everyones favorite casual game, this medieval style launcher is prepared to take down any castle. 8" x 5" print Also available as a $0.99 pinback button

name: Steampunk Dragon print
description: Stately brass and leather peer at you from this powerful firebreather. Print is 8" x 10" Also available as a $0.99 pinback button

name: "Home Is Where The Gaming Is" print
description: Playful and cute, this cross-stitch pattern is reminiscent of the best of 8-bit gaming, with nods to tabletop roleplay as well. Containing iconic images such as magic mushrooms, wizard hats, dice, pencils, and dragons, this will charm friend and foe alike. Print is 4" x 10" Also available as a tee-shirt

name: Cutie Dex-Starr button
description: Who wouldn't want a cute angry kitty shaking his fist angrily while pinned to your back? This pinback button will look adorable anywhere you put it.

name: Angry Dragons button
description: An Angry Birds parody, this original artwork by me takes the beloved game and turns into a mighty adventure! Also available as a 8" x 5" print

name: Cutie Cthulhu button
description: The center icon for my cthulhu damask pattern (available at Spoonflower), this 2.5" mylar covered pinback button will be a great addition to any cthulhu collection.

name: Wheaton's Law button
description: 2.5" mylar covered pinback button of Wheaton's Law (Seriously, don't be a dick, man). Background features the iconic colors and striping of the infamous Wesley Crusher sweater. Great reminder to friends and family exactly what you expect out of them.

name: Steampunk Dragon button
description: Beautiful original artwork (also available as a print) of a steampunk dragon, now in pinnable-to-your-pack form. 2.5" mylar coated pinback button featuring a hand-inked and digitally colored steampunk dragon in noble posing.

name: Blue Phone Box button
description:
Beautiful blue-on-blue-on-blue (it's blue all the way down!) of the modern iconic phone box from Doctor Who. Now you, too, can own a TARDIS*

2.5" pinback button with mylar coating

*Button may or may not be bigger on the inside. If you can get in...

name: GelCATinous Cube plushie
description: A five inch by five inche cube of durable foam covered in super-soft green fleece, with little dangly paws and cute face to die for, these gelCATinous cubes are entirely handmade and each sports unique and adorable quirks that makes each cat cube as individual as real cats.
